<h2 class="bold font-l">Night Fury</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Strike Class. The Unholy offspring of Lightning and Death itself. The Night Fury is known for its jet-black body good for camouflaging, streamlined for the incredibly speed it is known for. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OurDragonsAreDifferent" class='trope-example-link'>Our Dragons Are Different</a></p>
</div>
