<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="12jyp4" data-video-descrip="Hiccup thinks his father has found out about Toothless, his father is actually trying to congratulate him on doing well in dragon training. Things get awkward." data-video-title="Let's Talk About That Dragon" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/12jyp4_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/how_to_train_disneyscreencapscom_5742_6.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/OneDialogueTwoConversations" data-video-tropename="One Dialogue, Two Conversations" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/HowToTrainYourDragon" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/how_to_train_disneyscreencapscom_5742_6.jpg">
